"| `random` (gradientes independientes) | 0.089 / 0.911 | 0.080 / 0.920 | 0.138 / 0.862 | **0.045 / 0.965** |\n"
"| `pk1synth` (cielo tipo-PK1 (caída analítica)) | 0.130 / 0.985 | 0.130 / 0.985 | 0.108 / 0.993 | **0.0053 / 1.000** |\n"
