"\" [9136]: \"    {\n"
"\" [9137]: \"      if(array[i] > threshold)\n"
"\" [9138]: \"        counter++;\n"
"\" [9139]: \"    }\n"
"\" [9140]: \"    ```\n"
"\" [9141]: \"5. Las sentencias `case` en la estructura `switch` no deben ser aditivas. No hagas:\n"
"\" [9142]: \"    ```C\n"
