"    ```bash\n"
"    $ sh tools/build-translations.sh --add\n"
"    ```\n"
"2. Cleanup the translated `.md` files :\n"
"    ```bash\n"
"    $ sh tools/build-translations.sh --remove\n"
"    ```\n"
